dt-option.default:
        The default value for the `-init searchPanes.dataLength` option is `30`, after 30 characters the cell will cut off the end and append with '...'.


		This is useful as it prevents the searchPanes cells becoming mishapen and overpopulated.





    $('#example').DataTable( {
        searchPanes: {
            dataLength: 15
        },    
		dom: 'Sfrtip'
    });
